3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses the dual-role of the relay signal and how it can potentially increase the capacity of the first hop, which is relevant to systems and control. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper does not explicitly mention multimedia, but the concept of overhearing transmissions could be relevant to multimedia applications. 
5. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - The paper does not explicitly mention cryptography and security, but the concept of overhearing transmissions could be relevant to security and privacy concerns in communication systems.
